content: Pretty handy and easy to use. I just wish it had more species. There are only about 360-370 birds listed. Costa Rica has over 850 species. There are birds I have found that I can't identify because they aren't on the list. Oh, and we saw a Harpy Eagle....can't miss it, but not on the list!!! Whaaaatttt???
Unfortunately the app failed to load on my Samsung Galaxy S5, so I cannot review the content. I'm disappointed as I think it would have been useful.
Lots of information, sounds and pictures. Very easy to use and totally worth it.
